Title: Daddy's Home 2 Official Trailer #2 (2017) Mark Wahlberg, Will Ferrell Comedy Movie HD
Comment: I had a little trouble figuring out who's related to whom and why the living arrangements are as they are, but that's my fault for not watching Daddy's Home 1. This film is pretty much what you would expect a Christmas comedy with Will Farrell, Mark Wahlberg, John Lithgow and Mel Gibson to be: reasonably entertaining romp in which each actor portrays exactly the character we expect from him. The only aspect of the film that deserves a second or third thought lies in its portrayal of the complicated families a lot of us live in now. Multiple people involved in the parenting process means opportunity for conflict and cooperation. One charming detail near the end marks this as a film for 2017, no "It's a Wonderful Life," nor even "The Santa Clause," and that is the grinning boy who stands in line with all the girls waiting for his chance to kiss Dylan under the mistletoe.
